Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有輛直線加速很快的車追上來了 稍等一下吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,R32 GTR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就試試你有多少斤兩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就對了 就該這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(260,265)\fs20\fad(600,500)}新的挑戰者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送到這裏就行了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.81,0:02:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 我家就在那兒進去不遠處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.69,0:03:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 雖說你的車很舊 但我喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑起來有力 精緻可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TRUENO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TRUENO啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我還坐TRUENO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我很開心 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.02,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見 電話聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說你可愛哦 怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能跟得上高橋涼介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這輛GTR果然是無敵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.61,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管駕駛者技術再好 始終是舊款的FC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣已經是極限了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫高橋涼介 REDSUNS的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 我叫中裏毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個叫Night Kids的妙義山車隊成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Night Kids的中裏毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個妙義山下山最快的車手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是榮幸 超極巨星高橋涼介居然知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但據我所知 Night Kids的中裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是開S13的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙義的車手來秋名做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.81,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還問別人 你自己還不是赤城的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概都是為了同一個目的而來的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.91,0:05:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了要遇上昨天的86而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.81,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想用32吞掉86?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這輛改裝到三百八十匹馬力的32...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些我還是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從直線加速和排氣聲就能看出馬力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過結果很明顯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上山86絕不是32的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但下山無論如何你的32都贏不了那輛86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼? 我的32下山會輸給86?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別生氣 我只是實話實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你那麼懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弟弟輸了也不用那麼害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手只是輛86而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那小子賽一下就會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我能贏他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑 就憑你這句話我說什麼也不能退縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要贏了那輛86讓你收回剛才的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你囂張不了多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了妙義有我中裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.87,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓你知道轉子引擎根本不是32的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是開S13的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 從那時起我就改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 怎麼都超不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎道追上 一到直路又被甩開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以車手的技術來說我更勝一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 絕不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這輛車再怎麼拼都無法和32相提並論嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,號稱妙義山頭號下山車手的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然輸給了不能漂移的32
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車是有極限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論車手的身手再好 也無法超越車的極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算那輛86也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給 池谷前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸豆腐塊 昨天沒賣完 老爸叫我帶給前輩的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放冰箱裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你五年前就去秋名湖送豆腐的事 是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.26,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太見外了拓海 居然瞞著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可傳出去的話會惹不少麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.15,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五年前的話 我們只是青澀的中學一年級學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我的駕齡還長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中學時無論雨雪每天如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是在秋名的山道上開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凌晨的話不會碰到別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個意思 我是說遇到那樣的彎道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不覺得害怕嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...剛開始是很害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半年後恐懼感就漸漸消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度提升後很自然地輪胎開始打滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到能隨心所欲地滑行和停止又花了半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 只用一年就掌握了下山?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天開 滑行的緊張感很快就麻痹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.02,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊了 開始嘗試能貼護欄多近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正常人會做這麼危險的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒也不覺得這有多危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狀態好時能貼近到一厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不那樣找尋樂趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定會無聊死了 畢竟是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我從來沒想過要提高駕駛技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一心只想快點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有載著豆腐下山時 便盡可能快地猛跑回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.94,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 能問你件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,載著豆腐時怎麼跑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑太猛的話豆腐會碎掉吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上山時不能開太猛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爸在紙杯裏盛了水放在杯托上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.78,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跑時水不灑出來 再快豆腐也不會碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可這做起來非常困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始就算慢吞吞地跑水也會灑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剎車 方向盤 換檔 油門 無論哪個動作稍大水就灑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爸常說要讓水在紙杯中回轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓水在杯中回轉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於表面張力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.64,0:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晃起的水面會緊貼紙杯邊緣之處回轉半圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.19,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出彎時同樣 再讓水緊貼邊緣之處回轉就不會灑出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.17,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂移時能不讓杯裏的水灑出來花了相當長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂移時不讓水灑出來? 這種事有可能嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能的拓海 你在開玩笑吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.36,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制車最重要的基本就是重心移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實 漂移王土屋圭市在影片裏也是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行車時不讓紙杯裏的水灑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒掌握極精細的重心移動控制方法是辦不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更別提漂移了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事是不可能的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒說謊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小子 別因為贏了高橋啟介就得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹大爺我的眼睛可是雪亮...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來客人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高辛烷加滿 明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.69,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太厲害了 文太 這小子不只是山道車手那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 有件事拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能讓我坐你旁邊下一次秋名山嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊 反正沒什麼重要事
